## Methods I

<br> 

- Data on UNGA co-sponsorship by `r Citet(myBib, "lee2016shifting")` (1979-2014) $\rightarrow$ 36 weighted and directed networks

- $n \times n$ agreement matrix of annual co-sponsorship following `r Citet(myBib, "aleman2009comparing")`

- Agreement matrix of co-sponsoring at the UNGA in 1985 (first 5 rows and columns)

|          |    **AUS**   |    **AUT**   |    **BGD**   |    **BRB**   |    **CAN**   | $\cdots$ |
|:--------:|:--------:|:--------:|:--------:|:--------:|:--------:|:--------:|
|    **AUS**   |   1.00   |   **0.79**   |   0.61   |   0.35   |   0.79   | $\cdots$ |
